---
title: Welcome
description: Watch as Troy Vassalotti learns his way around a computer.
layout: primary
animation: true
pageName: homepage
---
<main class="layout">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="wrapper flex">
      <section class="welcome-screen" id="welcome">
        <div class="typewriter-container">
          <h1 class="typewriter typewriter_1">Hey, I'm Troy...</h1>
          <p class="typewriter typewriter_2">...and I make things.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="portrait">
          {% image './assets/img/me-on-set.jpg', 'This is me. I look like this.', [300, 600], ['webp', 'avif', 'jpg'], '(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 50vw', 'me'%}
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <p>I'm glad you could make it. Peruse my wares* and <a href="/about/">send me a letter</a> if you're so inclined.</p>
          <p class="disclaimer">I only accept bottlecaps as currency, sorry... (I'm kidding)</p>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="feed" id="posts">
        <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
        <div class="posts">
          <div class="grid full">
          {%- for post in collections.post.slice(collections.post.length - 5, collections.post.length) | reverse -%}
            <article class="post-listing">
              <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
              <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            </article>
          {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
        </div>
        {% button '/posts/', 'View All Posts', '' %}
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section class="projects" id="projects">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h2><span id="cool-anim">Cool</span> <span id="proj-anim">Projects</span></h2>
      <div class="showcase-container">
        <div class="showcase">
        {%- set imgWidths = [300, 800, 1400] -%}
        {%- set imgFormats = ['webp', 'jpg'] -%}
        {% for project in projects.homepage -%}
          {%- set projhref -%}{{ project.href }}{%- endset -%}
          {%- set projtitle -%}{{ project.title }}{%- endset -%}
          {%- set projimg -%}{{ project.img }}{%- endset -%}
          {%- set projalt -%}{{ project.alt }}{%- endset -%}
          {%- set projsrc = "./assets/img/" + projimg + "1920x1080.jpeg" -%}
          {%- captionOverlay projhref, projtitle -%}
            {%- imageSync projsrc, projalt, imgWidths, imgFormats, '(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 1200px', 'caption-image' -%}
          {%- endcaptionOverlay -%}
        {% endfor -%}
        </div>
        <section class="flex-center col center content">
          <div class="skewed-background">
            <div class="content">
              <p>These are only some of my projects, but I have more. Want to see them?</p>
              {% button '/projects/', 'More Projects', '' %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="supplemental" id="more">
    <div id="clouds">
      <div class="cloud foreground"></div>
      <div class="cloud background"></div>
      <div class="cloud foreground"></div>
      <div class="cloud background"></div>
      <div class="cloud foreground"></div>
      <div class="cloud background"></div>
      <div class="cloud background"></div>
      <div class="cloud foreground"></div>
      <div class="cloud background"></div>
      <div class="cloud background"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="sundial">
        <button title="Turn the clouds on or off." id="sundial" type="button" name="sundial">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--whitePrimary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"></circle><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"></line><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"></line><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"></line><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"></line><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"></line><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"></line><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"></line><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"></line></svg>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <div class="music" id="music">
          <h2>I Also Have Music</h2>
          <p>When Iâ€™m not coding, maybe I'm writing. My friends and I started <span class="bold">Front Royal</span> with the desire to make a name for ourselves, and I started <span class="bold">troy.</span> to explore a new outlet.</p>
          {% button '/music/', 'Peek That Music', '' %}
        </div>
        <div class="about" id="about">
          <h2>Looking For More?</h2>
          <p>You can find more on my <a class="animated-link" href="/about/">about</a> page.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <svg class="curve" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" x="0px" y="0px" viewBox="0 0 720 80">
      <path d="M0,80V47.6C0,47.6,333,0,503,0c166,0,217,24.3,217,24.3V80H0z"/>
    </svg>
  </section>
</main>
